g over the green grass his legs carrying him faster and faster you have been spotted and when you and your special friend finally meet you cling together in joyous reunion never to be parted again the happy kisses rain upon your face your hands again caress the beloved head and you look once more into the trusting eyes of your pet so long gone from your life but never absent from your heart then you cross rainbow bridge together author unknown Kodocha Cliff Richard Pitaten Shaggy dog story The Amber Spyglass Salad Fingers Care Bears Cat EastEnders W.I.T.C.H. Spidey Super Stories Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Sin City Friends Stomach cancer Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Knots Landing Neighbours Jon Secada Aerial (dance move) Diving Professional wrestling holds Frankie Laine Shen Gong Wu Dead Like Me Piccolo Junior Saga The Lovely Bones Guinea pig Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Past teachings of Prem Rawat Little Britain Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Babe Ruth The Rock and Roll Hall of Fame's 500 Songs that Shaped Rock and Roll Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories Minor characters in Teen Titans (animated series) The Pilgrim's Progress Charles Darwin's illness Dog training Hamster Muslim ibn Aqeel AFI 100 Years series Too Short a Season (TNG episode) Pysanka Rainbow Oasis (band) Garfield The Wizard of Oz (1939 film) Professional wrestling throws First aid The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe The McGuire Sisters Doris Day Operation Market Garden Breaststroke Time Out of Mind Yu-Gi-Oh! anime and manga characters YuYu Hakusho Marilyn Monroe Charles Darwin's views on religion Fancy Crane Humphrey Bogart Rich Mullins Characters of The Sandman Tenshinhan The Inside Phoebe Buffay's songs Joseph (Hebrew Bible) Fast bowling Book of Isaiah Comanche Mattress Waking the Dragons Darwin from Insectivorous plants to Worms Butterfly stroke Professional wrestling double-team maneuvers The Shining (film) Rocko's Modern Life Equine conformation Codename: Kids Next Door Dean Koontz Pr